Third Department,

August, 1978

(August 4, 1978) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Paul Hunt, Petitioner, v Lady R. Rucinski, as Superintendent of Albany County Jail, et al., Respondents.

—Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd [b], par 2), for a writ of habeas corpus denied as insufficient. Mahoney, P. J., Greenblott, Sweeney and Kane, JJ., concur.
